<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q22_v2" title="Q22_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>La diagonal de un prisma recto de base rectangular se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:msqrt>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msup><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:msup><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:msup><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:msqrt>
      </m:math>, con a, b y c las medidas de sus aristas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Se tiene un gran contenedor rectangular que aloja en su interior otro contenedor, también rectangular y paralelo al primero. Un tirante metálico une un vértice del contenedor grande con el vértice opuesto del contenedor pequeño y mide 20 cm en total. De esa longitud, 7 cm quedan fuera del contenedor pequeño, por lo que el tramo del tirante que recorre el interior del contenedor pequeño coincide con la diagonal de este prisma. En el contenedor pequeño, dos de sus aristas miden 3 cm y 4 cm.
      
      ¿Cuánto mide la tercera arista del contenedor pequeño?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">5 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El tramo interior del tirante mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que la diagonal del contenedor pequeño es 13 cm. Si la tercera arista fuera 5 cm, la diagonal sería <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:math><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> no es 13.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">12 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El tramo interior del tirante mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto la diagonal del contenedor pequeño es 13 cm. Si sus aristas miden 3 cm, 4 cm y <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Al cuadrar, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>169</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>144</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">10 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El tramo interior del tirante mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que la diagonal del contenedor pequeño debe ser 13 cm. Si la tercera arista fuera 10 cm, la diagonal sería <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:math><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>125</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>125</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> no es 13.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">13 cm<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El tramo interior del tirante mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que la diagonal del contenedor pequeño es 13 cm, no una arista. Si la tercera arista fuera 13 cm, la diagonal sería <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:math><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>169</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>194</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>194</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> no es 13.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la diagonal del contenedor pequeño</strong></p>
            <p>El tirante mide 20 cm en total y 7 cm quedan fuera del contenedor pequeño.</p>
            <p>Entonces, el tramo que recorre el interior del contenedor pequeño mide:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Ese tramo coincide con la diagonal del prisma pequeño, así que su diagonal mide 13 cm.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Plantear la fórmula de la diagonal</strong></p>
            <p>Las aristas del contenedor pequeño miden 3 cm, 4 cm y una tercera arista que llamaremos <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La diagonal de un prisma rectangular se calcula con:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                      <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                      <m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                      <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                      <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Elevar al cuadrado y despejar</strong></p>
            <p>Al cuadrar ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mn>13</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Calculamos los cuadrados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>169</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Sumamos:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>169</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Restamos 25 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>169</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>25</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>144</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Obtener la medida de la arista</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msqrt><m:mn>144</m:mn></m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como una arista es una longitud, tomamos el valor positivo.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La tercera arista del contenedor pequeño mide 12 cm.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>